data.description: Looking for a move-in ready home in the Maroa-Forsyth school district? This one is for you! Backing up to Fairway #5 at the Hickory Point Golf Course, is this spacious, all brick ranch nestled in Montezuma Hills Subdivision. Offering 3 bedrooms, each with their own walk in closet & en-suite featuring quartz vanity tops. Open concept living & dining room. A large family room with a fireplace & built in bookshelves. Eat in kitchen with new backsplash and stainless steel appliances. Atrium in the center of the house, with the right amount of sunlight shining through. Step into the oversized sun room, fully equipped with a wet bar, that leads you to a deck and large backyard, perfect for entertaining! This home has something for everyone & gives you ample space & opportunity to make it your own. Call today before its gone!
